312	// Considering delimiters (both leading and trailing), the span can consist of
313	// four positions:
314	//
315	// [ '       '                    syll             '                 '        ']
316	//   ^        ^                                    ^                           ^
317	//   | start  |leading_delim_end                   |trailing_delim_start
318	//   |trailing_delim_end=end
